air:Brand.Name: Economy Light
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Light
Econ Light
air:Brand.air:Text:
From an aperitif to a snack to a hot meal. The culinary offer in Economy Class Europe is determined by the length of the flight. All drinks are free of charge. Modern and comfortable seats offer a maximum of relaxation.
Economy Light:
▪ 1 piece of hand baggage up to 8 kg ▪ Snacks and beverages ▪ Miles
If the flight will be operated by another airline, then there maybe differences in the onboard product or service.
Economy Light

air:Brand.Name: Economy Saver
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Saver
Econ SAVER
air:Brand.air:Text:
LOT Economy Saver fares include the option to both cancel or rebook for a fee.
▪ 1 checked bag up to 23 kg included. ▪ 1 carry on bag up to 8 kg included. ▪ Water and snacks included. ▪ Meals and soft drinks available to purchase on board.
Always good deals

air:Brand.Name: LIGHT AND RELAX
air:Brand.air:Title: Light and Relax
LightRelax
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade to Light and Relax in order to check in a bag for free

For a small supplement over Check and Go fares, Light and Relax offers you additional comfort and you will also enjoy some flexibility.
• 1 piece hand baggage (12kg) + 1 accessory (eg. laptop case) + 1 piece checked baggage (23kg) • Free change to an earlier return flight on the same day, subject to availability • Free seat reservation (as from booking) • Online check in and free eNewspapers • Renewed buy on board selection • Loyalty miles accrual and redemption
If the flight will be operated by a partner airline, onboard product or service might differ.
Light and Relax. More travel, less hassle

air:Brand.Name: FLEX AND FAST
air:Brand.air:Title: Flex and Fast
Flex Fast
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade to Flex and Fast for priority check in, fast track and full flexibility

Flex and Fast is our premium economy class fare that allows full flexibility, priority on the ground and more comfort and services on board.
• 1 piece hand baggage (12kg) + 1 accessory (eg. laptop case) + 1 piece checked baggage (23kg) • Full flexibility • Free seat reservation (as from booking) • Online check in and free eNewspapers • Priority check in; Fast Lane at security; Priority boarding and disembarkation • Upgraded catering concept • Seating at front of aircraft • Free newspapers on board • Access to lounge at Brussels Airport for €25 • Loyalty miles accrual and redemption
If the flight will be operated by a partner airline, onboard product or service might differ.
Flex and Fast. More flexibility, less stress

air:Brand.Name: Economy Flex
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Flex
Econ FLEX
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade to Economy Flex for free of charge changes and refunds

Economy Flex fares are just as they sound - flexibility to amend or cancel your reservation free of charge when needed.
▪ Free of charge changes or refunds. ▪ 1 checked bag up to 23 kg included. ▪ 1 carry on bag up to 8 kg included. ▪ Water and snacks included. Meals and soft drinks available to purchase on board.
Additional flexibility when needed

air:Brand.Name: Fully Flex
air:Brand.air:Title: PLUS FLEX
FF
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade to Fully-Flex for complete flexibility and control to change your travel plans

Fully Flex includes
• Complete flexibility * please refer to fare rules • 23kgs checked baggage allowance • Standard Hand Baggage allowance • Contoured leather seats and generous leg room • Select your seat at any time • Complimentary newspapers on most flights • Complimentary drinks and snacks on every flight • Family-friendly features and kids' activity packs
Upgrade to Fully-Flex for complete flexibility and control to change your travel plans

air:Brand.Name: Economy Flex
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Flex
Eco Flex
air:Brand.air:Text: Need more flexibility in your travel plans? Upgrade to Economy Flex

The Flex fare is for passengers who need more flexibilty in their travel planning such as rebooking or refund.
Services included:
▪ 1 piece of hand luggage up to 8 kg ▪ 1 piece of checked baggage up to 23 kg ▪ Snacks and drinks ▪ Advanced seat reservation ▪ Award and status miles (+50 % award miles) ▪ Rebooking for free ▪ Change to earlier myAustrian flight same day
Economy Flex

air:Brand.Name: GoLight
air:Brand.air:Title: GoLight
GoLight
air:Brand.air:Text:
Choose Aegean, Europes Best Regional Airline, and discover why customers come back to us time after time.
GoLight fares offer the best deals, with passengers to receive Aegean’s full service benefits on board and on the ground.
- checked baggage available at a fee if required - hand luggage included (1 bag up to 8 kg) - complimentary Greek Cuisine meal and drinks on board - mileage accrual - check-in 48 hours - 30 min. before departure
The best fares, without bags

air:Brand.Name: Flex
air:Brand.air:Title: Flex
Flex
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade to Flex fares which include one free checked bag

Choose Aegean, Europes Best Regional Airline, and discover why customers come back to us time after time.
Passengers that need more flexibility when planning their journey and do not want to pay rebooking fees, can make unlimited changes. Also included are:
- 1 free checked baggage allowance (23kgs) - hand luggage included (1 bag up to 8 kg) - complimentary Greek Cuisine meal and drinks on board - mileage accrual - check-in 48 hours - 30 min. before departure
Full flexibility and bags included

air:Brand.Name: Checked Bag Included
air:Brand.air:Title: PLUS
CB
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade and take a checked bag at 23kgs

Checked Bag fare includes:
• 23kgs checked baggage • Standard hand baggage included • No change fee *difference in fare may apply • Free flight changes on the day of departure • Complimentary newspapers on most flights • Complimentary drinks and snacks on every flight • Family-friendly features and kids' activity packs
Take everything you need

air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Classic
EcoClassic
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade to Economy Classic if you desire free checked baggage and a seat reservation

The Classic fare is the standard fare with many services included such as free checked baggage, as well as an advanced seat reservation.
Services included:
▪ 1 piece of hand luggage up to 8 kg ▪ 1 piece of checked baggage up to 23 kg ▪ Snacks and drinks ▪ Advanced seat reservation ▪ Award and status miles
Economy Classic

Eco Light
air:Brand.air:Text:
The Light Fare covers the basic flight and is the most affordable choice for passengers who are travelling with hand luggage only and do not require rebooking and refund options.
Services included:
▪ 1 piece of hand luggage up to 8 kg ▪ Snacks and drinks ▪ Seat reservation at Check-in ▪ Award and status miles
